@startuml
actor User
participant CLI
participant CsvReader
participant TransportSolver
participant Simulation

User -> CLI: Запуск с параметром CSV
CLI -> CsvReader: read("data.csv")
CsvReader --> CLI: DataInput
CLI -> TransportSolver: solve()
TransportSolver --> CLI: TransportResult
CLI -> Simulation: run(10000, demand)
Simulation --> CLI: SimResult
CLI --> User: Вывод результатов
@enduml
